snippet.textDisplay:
Since I explored and discovered real beauty and talent of Pakistan, I am totally in love with it.After entering the extraordinary musical world of coke studio, I just got obsessed with it , I was eagerly waiting for new season but still had to rely upon old ones by Coke Studio, Finally, It is out now and it is amazing, It got a super courageous, delicate and strong feeling which can't be described in the worlds, It can be just felt:)  After seeing the beauty of your beautiful country Pakistan as I have been there, I am in love with your anthem as well, Being honest, The best national anthem I have ever heard....Can't wait to  have a musical journey alongwith beautiful cultural, lingual and ethnical colors of Pakistan,Your food, music, natural beauty, bravery, judiciary, diversity, cultures, languages, architectural heritage,army, intelligence, hospitality, lovely nature are just amazing, outstanding and  splendid.Simply, Just perfect..Can't wait to   visit Pakistan real soon again...
Thank You Pakistan,We love you
Long Live Pakistan 
From USA ......
Stay blessed😊
Any other American here?
